Ballast Nedam Wins Contract for Butendiek Offshore Wind Farm

-- B y   M a r t i j n   v a n   d e r   S t a r r e
-- 
2011-09-02T05:27:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/ballast-nedam-wins-contract-for-butendiek-offshore-wind-farm.html
Ballast Nedam (BALNE)  NV won a 250 million-
euro contract for the engineering, supply and installation of 80
foundations at the Butendiek offshore wind farm in  Germany , the
company said today in a statement.  “It is expected that financial close of the project is
achieved ultimately by the end of this year,” the Dutch company
said. Ballast Nedam sees good opportunities for further work in
the offshore wind market in the years to come, it also said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Martijn van der Starre at 
 vanderstarre@bloomberg.net  